{"tid":1440842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老味 班藍絲開始target班crew","createTime":"2019-08-10T14:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T16:04:57.000Z","uid":84331,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c959b8ffbbb1fc86711ddb1f2bd9ba761b2cdef5","tid":1440842,"uid":84331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:02:46.000Z","msg":"自從cx機長make咗個撐港人嘅PA<br />\n一連三日和你飛活動開始<br />\n琴日中共搵cx開刀個聲明一出<br />\n班藍絲就開始target班crew<br />\n想搞到佢地份工都冇埋<br />\n今曰已經傳緊Fb兩個Po <br />\n一個標題為支持非法集會嘅空姐空少<br />\n係有條片錄住幾個HX crew步出arrival hall果陣<br />\n舉手和應班接機嘅朋友 <br />\n另一個係個藍絲話8月5日坐某班HX嘅機返港時<br />\n個crew make PA時最後講左句「香港加油」<br />\n然後話要求貴公司回應個crew咁樣make PA<br />\n係咪得到公司認可<br />\n（兩個po我唔特別轉載係到 因為係有名同有樣）<br />\n我真係好擔心啲crew因為咁而俾公司拎黎開刀祭旗<br />\n我地係咪應該幫下佢地<br />\n話哂和你飛都係一班航空界嘅朋友帶頭搞起<br />\n當中都有好多好多crew係好支持呢兩個月嘅行動<br />\n冇理由因為表達下個人政治立場都要被炒！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed73a2184e5673885aae7c6a650e71560053117","tid":1440842,"uid":185960,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:03:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1LFMotPfcLCi5MXxioVQX2E32ovPvizhH?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1LFMotPfcLCi5MXxioVQX2E32ovPvizhH%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPIL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=97a9b5bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1LFMotPfcLCi5MXxioVQX2E32ovPvizhH?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n[文宣］黑白大字報 政權罪行 遍地開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360258</a><br />\n<br />\n文宣就係做比藍絲、港豬<br />\n做比自己人睇有撚用！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2b5085945b06da72c88aedf29c9da5b23c8bdf","tid":1440842,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":